@node Main "iTrix - Documentation"

                               'iTrix' 1.0

                           by Charles-N. Jacob

  'iTrix' is a @{" Workbench game " link play} where you have to move hexagonal
shaped tiles containing various patterns so that 2 tiles of the
same type are next and 'linked' to each other. When 2 tiles of the
same type are placed next to each other, they are then removed, and
the link that connect both tiles is also removed.

  As you complete a game board, iTrix displays a new board and the
game continues...

  Have fun!

